data.description: Cottage style charmer in the highly sought after Crofton Park subdivision in Broomfield. This perfectly situated 4 bedroom 3 bathroom home features a corner lot with access and unobstructed views to the Metzger Farm Open Space with plenty of walking/biking trails and pond right out your front door, plus a huge neighborhood park! Enjoy that morning cup of coffee or evening glass of wine on the upper balcony with views of the mountains, and enjoy cozy snowy nights by the living room fireplace. The renovations that have been done make this home one of the best in the neighborhood. Updated backyard with patio and stream lighting for amazing entertaining or just chilling out, new hardwood floors throughout, interior custom trim, staircase and paint. New roof, new exterior paint, newer appliances, new toilets, kitchen sink and garbage disposal. Partially finished basement for office or workout area, and separate storage. This is a must see, so schedule your showing now before it's too late!
